  "text": "Here we conduct another set of experiments where we compare MMO-CC with five CC algorithms, i.e., DECC-D [CITATION_1] , DECC-G [CITATION_2] , MLCC [CITATION_3] , CC-CMA-ES [CITATION_4] , and DECC-DML [CITATION_5] , that decompose a given problem with nondifferential method during coevolution.",
